ue to the **England vs Japan** match. The main entrance will be exit-only temporarily, with step-free access via an alternative entrance.([tfl.gov.uk](https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/))\n  - **Wembley Park Station**: Lift access from street to ticket hall is unavailable until **Autumn 2026**, though alternate level routes remain. Entry restrictions apply today due to the event; use Olympic Way for entry.([tfl.gov.uk](https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/))\n\n---\n\n##  Summary Table\n\n| Line / Station          | Current Status / Notice                                                                 |\n|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| Central Line            | Minor delays (Bond Street faulty train)                                                 |\n| DLR                     | Minor delays (fault near Westferry)                                                     |\n| Other Tube Lines        | Good service generally across the network                                               |\n| Barons Court Station    | Eastbound services suspended until 7 June                                               |\n| Victoria Station        | Reduced escalator access to Victoria line until late May                                |\n| Easter weekend closures | Bakerloo, District, Lioness, Hammersmith & City, and Waterloo & City lines affected     |\n| Accessibility issues    | Multiple stations with lift faults (see above)                                          |\n| Clapham Junction        | Footbridge works until Nov 2027 — allow extra time                                      |\n| Wembley Central/Park    | Event-related congestion, altered access, ongoing lift works                            |\n\n---\n\nLet me know if you'd like planned updates for specific dates or tailored assistance for your journey.","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tubenotifications.co.uk/line-status","start_index":265,"end_index":337,"title":"London Tube status: live updates | London Underground Alerter"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tubenotifications.co.uk/line-status","start_index":436,"end_index":508,"title":"London Tube status: live updates | London Underground Alerter"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tubenotifications.co.uk/line-status","start_index":625,"end_index":697,"title":"London Tube status: live updates | London Underground Alerter"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/victoria-station-delays-tfl-tube-b1276940.html","start_index":1117,"end_index":1222,"title":"London travel news LIVE: Victoria station repairs sparks delays to ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/","start_index":1369,"end_index":1431,"title":"Tube, Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR & Tram status updates - Transport ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.trafficdelays.co.uk/london-trains/","start_index":1819,"end_index":1890,"title":"London Tube, DLR, Overground, Tram and TfL Rail Service Status."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.trafficdelays.co.uk/london-trains/","start_index":2037,"end_index":2108,"title":"London Tube, DLR, Overground, Tram and TfL Rail Service Status."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.trafficdelays.co.uk/london-trains/","start_index":2403,"end_index":2474,"title":"London Tube, DLR, Overground, Tram and TfL Rail Service Status."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.trafficdelays.co.uk/london-trains/","start_index":2560,"end_index":2631,"title":"London Tube, DLR, Overground, Tram and TfL Rail Service Status."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.trafficdelays.co.uk/london-trains/","start_index":2812,"end_index":2883,"title":"London Tube, DLR, Overground, Tram and TfL Rail Service Status."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/","start_index":3249,"end_index":3311,"title":"Tube, Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR & Tram status updates - Transport ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/","start_index":3473,"end_index":3535,"title":"Tube, Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR & Tram status updates - Transport ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/","start_index":3754,"end_index":3816,"title":"Tube, Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR & Tram status updates - Transport ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/","start_index":4037,"end_index":4099,"title":"Tube, Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR & Tram status updates - Transport ..."}],"logprobs":[]}],"status":"completed"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":81}

